        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ben2 AI operates on a microservices-oriented architecture, allowing seamless integration with existing API gateways. Key components include the inference engine, which processes requests asynchronously, and a state management layer for handling concurrent sessions. To leverage Ben2, ensure your infrastructure supports gRPC or RESTful protocols, and configure load balancers to distribute traffic evenly across instances."
          }
